---
title: Double Striploin Steak and Sun-Dried Tomato Cream Sauce with Roasted Potatoes and Walnut-Topped Green Beans
description: Break out the fine china to feast tonight! Tender steak is topped with a creamy and umami-rich sun-dried tomato cream sauce in this lick-the-plate-clean dish. Walnuts, Parmesan and green beans make the perfect trio to balance out this luxe meal.
